TestCase.TestCase_Title: Cut and paste variables from one owned category to another

Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Create an administrator context called "AdminContext" and store it in D:\OrchestraFrameworkTests\Administrator
Create two categories "Category0" and "Category1" within the "AdminContext" context
Create a "Variable0" variable within the "Category0" category
Create a "FileVariable0" variable of type "FileVariable" within the "Category0" category
Create a "FolderVariable0" variable of type "FolderVariable" within the "Category0" category
Click on the "File" menu and select "Save"
Select the user mode by clicking on the "Mode" menu and selecting "User"
Create a participation to the "AdminContext" administrator context called "Participation to AdminContext"
Create two categories "Category2" and "Category3" within the "Participation to AdminContext" context
Create a "Variable0" variable within the "Category2" category
Create a "FileVariable0" variable of type "FileVariable" within the "Category2" category
Create a "FolderVariable0" variable of type "FolderVariable" within the "Category2" category
Click on the "File" menu and select "Save"
Select the administrator mode by clicking on the "Mode" menu and selecting "Administrator"
Unfold the "AdminContext" context in the context viewer
Click on the "Category0" category
In the variable viewer, select all variables
Right click on the "Variable0" variable and select "Cut"
Unfold the "AdminContext" context in the context viewer
Right click on the "Category1" category and select "Paste"

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: All variables have been added to Category1 in the variable viewer

Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Click on the "Category0" category

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: The variable viewer is empty

Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Click on the "File" menu and select "Save"
Select the user mode by clicking on the "Mode" menu and selecting "User"
Unfold the "Participation to AdminContext" context in the context viewer
Click on the "Category2" category
In the variable viewer, select all variables
Right click on the "Category3" category and select "Paste"

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: All variables have been added to Category3 in the variable viewer

Step_Description.Step_Description_label: Click on the "Category2" category

Step_ExpectedResult.Step_ExpectedResult_label: The variable viewer is empty
